 a Persian prince and ally of Belshazzar mentioned in the Book of Daniel. Since the early 1900s it has been one of the most enduringly popular boys' names in the English-speaking world.  See also  Michal ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Michele Zanche was born in 1204, in Sardinia, Italy. He had at least 1 daughter with Simona DORIA. He died in 1275, in his hometown, at the age of 71."},"et":{"1204–1275":"1204–1275","1221–Female":"1221–Surnud","1237–1316":"1237–1316","1316":"1316","1204":"1204","1237":"1237","1221":"1221","1275":"1275","Sardegna, Italia":"Sardegna, Itaalia","Logudura, Sardinia (owned by Spain), Italia":"Sardegna, Itaalia","Logudoro, Sardegna, Italie":"Logudoro, Sardegna, Itaalia"},"fi":{"1204–1275":"1204–1275","1221–Female":"1221–Kuollut","1237–1316":"1237–1316","1316":"1316","1204":"1204","1237":"1237","1221":"1221","1275":"1275","Sardegna, Italia":"Sardegna, Italia","Logudura, Sardinia (owned by Spain), Italia":"Sardegna, Italia","Logudoro, Sardegna, Italie":"Logudoro, Sardegna, Italia"},"fr":{"1204–1275":"1204–1275","1221–Female":"1221–Décédée","1237–1316":"1237–1316","1316":"1316","1204":"1204","1237":"1237","1221":"1221","1275":"1275","Sardegna, Italia":"Sardegna, Italie","Logudura, Sardinia (owned by Spain), Italia":"Sardegna, Italie","Logudoro, Sardegna, Italie":"Logudoro, Sardegna, Italie","lifeSummary":"Michele Zanche est né en 1204, à Sardegna, Italie. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Simona DORIA. Il est décédé en 1275, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 71 ans."},"de":{"1204–1275":"1204–1275","1221–Female":"1221–Verstorben","1237–1316":"1237–1316","1316":"1316","1204":"1204","1237":"1237","1221":"1221","1275":"1275","Sardegna, Italia":"Sardinien, Italien","Logudura, Sardinia (owned by Spain), Italia":"Sardinien, Italien","Logudoro, Sardegna, Italie":"Logudoro, Sardinien, Italien","lifeSummary":"Michele Zanche wurde 1204 in Sardinien, Italien geboren. Er hatte mit Simona DORIA mindestens 1 Tochter. Er starb 1275 im Alter von 71 Jahren in seinem Geburtso